{"tid":1113042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士奇異事件","createTime":"2019-04-17T17:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T19:30:54.000Z","uid":240863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"576a35193d4b80e084b2a9f954bd949221d747df","tid":1113042,"uid":240863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:53:50.000Z","msg":"上次搭巴士出機場訓著咗覺 <br />\n去到青馬收費廣場個站<br />\n突然隔離個嬸嬸無啦啦拍醒我 <br />\n我以為咩事<br />\n點知佢問我：你訓著左 你唔驚訓過龍咩？<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我話唔驚<br />\n唔該哂你 ⋯<br />\n<br />\n佢話：哦 咁你繼續訓啦 <br />\n<br />\n但個刻已經冇意欲想訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我拎起部電話碌吓 <br />\n嬸嬸又再講：嘈醒你唔好意思呀<br />\n<br />\n我話唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾著係你地 會點做？<br />\n真係好多奇怪嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f327bf3500beeaa3a8a027459233b195a9e7cf","tid":1113042,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T19:30:54.000Z","msg":"係咪驚你暈左"}]}